{"tid":1810130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國防長蓬佩奧稱與中央政治委員楊潔篪對話談特朗普下令殺死蘇萊馬尼的決定","createTime":"2020-01-03T15:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T16:36:57.000Z","uid":125193,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"37f03c078ba02159df2f1d221c22d10020b16980","tid":1810130,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:05:19.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧在社交網站表示，他與中共中央政治局委員、中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪對話，討論有關總統特朗普，下令殺死伊朗革命衛隊高級指揮官蘇萊馬尼的決定。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又與英國外相藍韜文，以及德國外長馬斯對話，強調有關決定是防禦行動，目的是消除蘇萊馬尼對美國迫切的威脅。他說，感謝盟友意識到伊朗特種部隊「聖城旅」不斷構成的侵略性威脅，重申美國致力緩和緊張局勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TN3n5wg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTN3n5wg.jpg&h=8d517a4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e26a37905cf93d15d60c1a66aa5df05e0d5ade86","tid":1810130,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500907-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500907-20200103.htm&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=201ea866\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500907-20200103.htm&h=83512bfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500907-20200103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"96d1c3960ea565c841beea3cb59ff22ebf57345f","tid":1810130,"uid":97518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"美國佬癲起上黎，支共真係蚊比同牛比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7974c9f214092ed20b1bee8363a27eb0f96578b3","tid":1810130,"uid":130693,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:43